<-------------------> this all are very important topics <---------------------------->

1. What is Abstraction
2. Abstract Keyword

<---------------------------------Explaination---------------------------------------->

1. What is Abstraction
-> Abstraction ka matlab hai ki jitna tumko dhikna chaiye ham utna hi dhikayenge matlab ham implementation
nhai batayenge bas whai chiz dhikayenge jo apko jarruri hai dhekna .
-> implementation detail abstract out kardi gai hai matlab hamne usko kaise banaya hai wo nhai batayenge
hamm tumko utna hi dhikayenge jitna tumko dhikna chaiye bas kyu ki utna hi jaruri hai tumko dhikna wo
chal kaise raha hai usse kya matalab tumko .
-> Shade simple bhasa me jo use karega usko sirf feature bataye jayenge naahi implementation .
-> hame iss chiz ka dhyan rhakna hai ki minimum details dete hue or maximum functionalatiy kaise
deni hai isme jyada dhyan rhakna hai .
-> user ko sirf ye dhyan dena hai ki object mere liye kya kar shakta hai wo kaam kaise kar raha hai
uspe user ko dhya nhai rhakna hai.
-> user ko ham sirf key or value wale chizze dhikayenge and sirf whai access denge key value wale methods
ki bahut hi bhaidya .

2. Abstract Keyword
-> Abstract ka matlab hai ki implementation ko hide karna and only features dhikana .
-> ham chae to class ko bhi abstract bana shakte hai or chae to method ko bhi abstract bana shakte
hai .
-> agar ham log class ko object banaayenge to koi bhi uss class ko object nhai bana paeyga uss class
ki properties and methods ko inherit karna padega
-> agar hamne kisi class ko abstract bana diya to iska matlab ki wo sirf bata shakta hai ki wo chizz
kaise banegi or jo wo chizz ko banayega usko hi bolenge ham object but abstract class bana ne ke baad
ham uska object nhai bana pate hai isliye hame abstract class ko extend karna hai padta hai jise ham
inherit bhi bolte hai.
-> abstract class hi ham log isliye bante hai ki ham use inherit kar paye bass .
